import React from 'react'
import { Col, Container, Row } from 'react-bootstrap'
import './style.css'

export default function Menu() {
    return (
        <Container>
            <Row></Row>
            <Row>
                <Col></Col>
                <Col></Col>
                <Col></Col>
                <Col></Col>
                <Col></Col>
                <Col></Col>
            </Row>
        </Container>
    )
}
